Syntax file (for include only)
Language:    Mojo epl/ep templats stored in  Perl __DATA__
By Yaroslav Korhsak <ykorshak@gmail.com>

For highligh ep/epl templates in __DATA__ and *.html.ep/epl files,
save this fils into ~/.vim/ and add following line to your .vimrc:

" Enables __DATA__ highlighting for perl files
autocmd FileType perl syn include @perlDATA syntax/MojoliciousTemplate.vim

possible configuration:
:let mojo_disable_html = 1

